
Appraise <object>
cost: 10 spell points.

Since thieves handle a great many items, they learn the fine art of
appraisal so they may cull the valuable items from the invaluable
ones.  A thief's abaility to appraise an object rises 5% for each
level earned, and is modified by the thief's intelligence. Thieves have
been known to give erroneous appraisals from time to time.

In order to appraise an object, the object must be in their inventory,

